NT face=Tahoma size=2><B>From:</B> David Stern \n[mailto:david.stern@asiagateway.co.uk] <BR><B>Sent:</B> Saturday, May 10, 2008 \n11:17 AM<BR><B>To:</B> Lesley Groff<BR><B>Subject:</B> AGC<BR></FONT><BR></DIV>\n<DIV></DIV>Dear Jeffrey,\n<DIV><BR></DIV>\n<DIV>Was great seeing you again on Friday, thank you for taking the time!</DIV>\n<DIV><BR></DIV>\n<DIV>As discussed I attach the overview of AGC Capital.&nbsp;</DIV>\n<DIV>I would be delighted and honoured if you would participate.</DIV>\n<DIV><BR></DIV>\n<DIV>In any case, my search for the book for you continues....</DIV>\n<DIV><BR></DIV>\n<DIV>All the best</DIV>\n<DIV>David</DIV>\n<DIV><BR></DIV>\n<DIV>\n<DIV>\n<DIV></DIV></DIV></DIV></BODY></HTML>\n","is_from_epstein":false,"attachments":2,"avatar_color":"#0f9d58","stars":2,"is_redacted":false}]